1
00:00:16,566 --> 00:00:18,119
All right, oars up.

2
00:00:21,139 --> 00:00:23,139
Welcome to Rocky Point, boys.

3
00:00:24,055 --> 00:00:25,184
Bring her in.

4
00:00:26,461 --> 00:00:28,461
(men chattering)

5
00:00:29,936 --> 00:00:30,909
Another one.

6
00:00:31,836 --> 00:00:32,898
Got it.

7
00:00:34,649 --> 00:00:36,649
- What now?
- We go visit an old friend.

8
00:00:37,824 --> 00:00:38,561
Come on.

9
00:00:40,620 --> 00:00:44,756
Our target lives in the hamlet
known as Rocky Point.

10
00:00:45,873 --> 00:00:47,907
He's a former resident of Setauket

11
00:00:48,956 --> 00:00:50,424
using his wealth and standing

12
00:00:50,459 --> 00:00:52,924
to masquerade as a Tory,

13
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:55,510
hiding in plain sight.

14
00:00:59,012 --> 00:01:02,013
Today we rein in this traitor

15
00:01:02,065 --> 00:01:04,415
quietly poisoning the countryside.

16
00:01:05,018 --> 00:01:08,792
His name is Samuel Culper.

17
00:01:10,490 --> 00:01:11,856
- <i> (door bursts open)</i>
- (screams)

18
00:01:11,908 --> 00:01:13,074
Don't move! Don't move!

19
00:01:13,110 --> 00:01:16,828
- Don't move!
- (guns cocking)

20
00:01:18,582 --> 00:01:20,331
Caleb Brewster?

21
00:01:20,367 --> 00:01:22,534
Hello, Beekman.

22
00:01:22,536 --> 00:01:24,252
You men will leave with me.

23
00:01:24,287 --> 00:01:26,168
The rest of the unit
will keep their posts.

24
00:01:26,706 --> 00:01:28,561
We shall return after daybreak tomorrow.

25
00:01:28,721 --> 00:01:31,593
Sir, all this for one man?

26
00:01:31,628 --> 00:01:34,929
Kill a Queen's Ranger? Are you insane?

27
00:01:34,965 --> 00:01:38,383
A touch. But I wouldn't worry
yourself about this one.

28
00:01:38,385 --> 00:01:40,118
<i>He'll be dead before
he knows what hit him.</i>

29
00:01:40,170 --> 00:01:43,293
I imagine it will be quite
the surprise for him.

30
00:01:44,774 --> 00:01:45,940
Fall out!

31
00:01:52,099 --> 00:01:54,232
(Robert growls)

32
00:01:55,905 --> 00:01:56,885
Ah.

33
00:01:58,371 --> 00:02:00,437
Dead man marching.

